					<h5><b><u>The Law Offices of Stoody &amp; Mills</u></b><br>

				  </h5>

<center><img src="imgs/smd.jpg"></center>

					<p align="center"> Stoody &amp; Mills specializes in the defense of Workers&rsquo; Compensation matters, whether they are self-insured employers or insurance carriers. We represent some of the most respected businesses and insurance companies in Southern California. The firm covers several Workers&rsquo; Compensation Appeal Boards including: Ventura County, Los Angeles County, Orange County, Riverside County and San Diego County.</p>
					<p align="center">Since its founding in 2001, the firm has specialized in the representation of many types of employers in defense of their Workers&rsquo; Compensation matters, as well as defending Labor Code Section 132a actions and claims for Serious &amp; Willful Misconduct. Our firm has also been retained as a Workers&rsquo; Compensation Expert Witness on civil matters and has testified in court on many occasions.<br>
					  
